text: Nikolayevka () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Nikolayevsky Selsoviet, Narimanovsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 1,598 as of 2010. There are 6 streets. == Geography == It is located 24 km from Astrakhan, 54 km from Narimanov. == References == Category:Rural localities in Narimanovsky District
title: Nikolayevka, Narimanovsky District, Astrakhan Oblast
